{"tid":1747821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［大海撈針］幫手搵一絲打","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T11:54:24.000Z","uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f749073cdb1d454404a52db9b6632568c1e1b5e","tid":1747821,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"話說有個絲打一直同我有聯絡，都有發開夢<br />\n間唔時都會報平安，但係早幾日同佢TG傾傾下突然冇再睇過我訊息（麻煩排除佢唔想應我呢點，因為通常都係關心&amp;盡量支援佢）<br />\n因為避免佢對我有懷疑，所以起初到而家都冇點交換過個人資料，我只係俾過我手提電話號碼佢，有突發事就搵我幫忙<br />\n<br />\n詳細唔講太多，希望有人識佢本人/知道佢係咪俾人拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢連登個名：踎低起身見羅文<br />\n<br />\n20號上晝就冇再覆過，幫幫手 <br />\n冇佢名冇佢電話唔知佢最後係邊⋯⋯"},{"pid":"f37d3e3835f7cb14170ce0be2a1028366056048c","tid":1747821,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b257fd64f14cd7e882f7ec88fa43874a06b6a46","tid":1747821,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:37:56.000Z","msg":"推兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58ebb3c824868db419dbf8f811869faeb47be60","tid":1747821,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"推三下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61a0672a6a6c14253930da9a5119cc5d24736c7","tid":1747821,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"推四下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3aefb1f420f8f57c85e203b7d8e428b416fbe7","tid":1747821,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"推五下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7326fd8c1833c31dc6a45350677101206a0192d5","tid":1747821,"uid":215293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy